&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Report: Data breaches not uncommon in last five years&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sensitive information from nearly 3.4 million Massachusetts customer accounts has been inappropriately viewed, lost or stolen from businesses and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.sentinelandenterprise.com/news/ci_30759162/report-data-breaches-not-uncommon-last-five-years&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.sentinelandenterprise.com/news/ci_30759162/report-data-breaches-not-uncommon-last-five-years&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breaches soar as Scottish firms fail to take precautions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;REPORTS of data and cyber security incidents have risen by a fifth in a year, with fears expressed that sweeping new pan-European privacy rules &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.heraldscotland.com/News/15055594.Data_breaches_soar_as_Scottish_firms_fail_to_take_precautions/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.heraldscotland.com/News/15055594.Data_breaches_soar_as_Scottish_firms_fail_to_take_precautions/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Online Security Survey: Six in Ten Americans are Data Breach Victims&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nearly two-thirds of Americans (64%) have personally been victims of data breaches, Pew&amp;rsquo;s Kenneth Olmstead and Aaron Smith highlight in a Jan.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.telecompetitor.com/online-security-survey-six-in-ten-americans-are-data-breach-victims/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.telecompetitor.com/online-security-survey-six-in-ten-americans-are-data-breach-victims/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
